@startuml
title PQR Hybrid Lakehouse - Contenedores y Dependencias (Docker Compose)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
top to bottom direction

package "Compose Base (docker-compose.yml)" {
  [postgres\npostgis/postgis:15-3.4] as pg
  [rustfs\nrustfs/rustfs:latest] as rustfs
  [dask-scheduler\ndaskdev/dask:latest] as dasks
  [dask-worker\ndaskdev/dask:latest] as daskw
  [prefect-server\nprefecthq/prefect:3-latest] as prefect
  [prometheus\nprom/prometheus] as prom
  [grafana\ngrafana/grafana] as grafana
  [streamlit\nlocal-streamlit] as streamlit
  [metabase\nmetabase/metabase] as metabase
}

package "Compose Overlay Supabase (docker-compose.supabase.yml)" {
  [kong\nkong:2.8.1] as kong
  [auth\nsupabase/gotrue:v2.186.0] as auth
  [rest\npostgrest/postgrest:v12.2.3] as rest
  [meta\nsupabase/postgres-meta:v0.95.2] as meta
  [supabase-studio\nsupabase/studio:2025.10.01-sha-8460121] as studio
}

database "postgres\nschemas: auth/meta/bronze/silver/gold" as db
storage "rustfs /data" as obj

pg --> db
rustfs --> obj

daskw --> rustfs : read/write objects
daskw --> pg : insert/upsert curated data
dasks --> daskw : scheduling
prefect --> dasks : orchestration
prefect --> pg : metadata/state

prom --> dasks : scrape metrics
grafana --> prom : dashboards

streamlit --> pg : kpi queries
metabase --> pg : sql exploration

kong --> auth : /auth/*
kong --> rest : /rest/v1/*
studio --> meta : schema browser
meta --> pg : metadata SQL
auth --> pg : auth schema
rest --> pg : REST over tables/views

auth ..> pg : depends_on healthy
rest ..> pg : depends_on healthy
meta ..> pg : depends_on healthy
metabase ..> pg : depends_on healthy
daskw ..> dasks : depends_on healthy
studio ..> kong : depends_on
studio ..> meta : depends_on

note right of studio
OPENAI_API_KEY opcional para AI Assistant
en Studio.
end note

@enduml
